---
import HSWicons from "./HSWicons.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import aboutImage from "../assets/about.webp";
---

<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl py-4 px-4 ">
  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 md:items-start">
    <!-- Izquierda -->
    <div class="">
      <h1 class="bs-h2 text-[color:var(--accent-dark)]">About</h1>
      
        <p class="mt-8 text-lg leading-7 text-black">
          Born from a 13,000-foot volcanic aquifer beneath the Big Island,
          Hawaiian Springs Water begins as pure rainfall that seeps through
          thousands of feet of ancient lava rock. Over years, it is naturally
          filtered and enriched with essential minerals, emerging as a smooth,
          naturally alkaline water that captures the true taste of Hawaii.
          Bottled directly at the source, untouched and unaltered, every drop
          reflects the islandâ€™s volcanic origin, pristine nature, and timeless
          purity.
        </p>
      
    </div>

    <!-- Derecha -->
    <div class="max-w-md md:ml-auto self-start">
      <Image
        src={aboutImage}
        alt="About Image"
        class="mt-10 rounded-xl shadow-lg"
        width={600}
        height={600}
        loading="eager"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
  <HSWicons />
</section>
